@startuml View_Equipment_Reports_State_Diagram
title View Equipment Reports - State Diagram
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false

[*] --> ReportRequested : Admin opens report page

ReportRequested --> AccessChecking : Check admin permission
AccessChecking --> LoadingData : Permission valid
AccessChecking --> AccessDenied : Permission invalid

LoadingData --> CalculatingStatistics : Load equipment and issue data
CalculatingStatistics --> ReportReady : Build report data
ReportReady --> ReportDisplayed : Display report page

ReportDisplayed --> LoadingData : Change page or refresh report

AccessDenied --> [*]
ReportDisplayed --> [*]

@enduml
